<DATELINE>HAMDEN, Conn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Fire broke out in the first-floor library
of an eight-story apartment complex for the elderly, injuring 36,
officials said.
   Five of the injured were in critical condition, hospital
officials said.
