<HEAD>Two Instructors Eject From Navy Jet That Crashed in Woods</HEAD>
<DATELINE>GROVE HILL, Ala. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Two instructors ejected from a TA4J
Skyhawk Navy training jet that crashed Thursday in a forest,
authorities said.
   A search helicopter went to the scene in search of the pilot and
co-pilot, said Lt. j.g. Mary Chamberlin, spokeswoman for the
